  "text": "Given the lack of such information, we applied a newly developed Australian dietary index, the DGI 6 [CITATION_1] , to investigate longitudinal change in diet quality and its association with socio-demographic and lifestyle characteristics in participants of a 15-y follow-up study. Further, we examined whether there was an association between period of birth (birth cohort) and diet quality in this population.",
